populatePreferences

public void populatePreferences(Map<String,List<ProbeFunc<Integer>>> features)
Populates the feature preferences from a map of Strings, representing categories, to lists of probe functions. The toString method of the probe function is used to name the corresponding preference.

This method is called when the Proximity Service is connected to this activity.

Parameters:
features -
